  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the real value of a fast track protocol compared to a standard care protocol
      regarding postoperative complications and hospital stay in a multicentric setting in an
      intention to treat fashion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Our fast track protocol contains the four major components perioperative fluid restriction,
      epidural analgesia, early oral feeding and enforced mobilisation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
